Since $AB$ is the base of triangle $ABC,$ $C$ must be on one of the horizontal lines passing through the remaining $4$ points to the left of $AB,$ or the $4$ points to the right of $AB.$

[asy]
draw((0,0)--(0,6)--(6,6)--(6,0)--cycle,linewidth(1));
for(int i=1;i<6;++i)
